Appling conditional aggregation ===> We can identiy specific set of records using case statment by populating 1 and 0.

SELECT
OrderID,
Sales,
CASE WHEN Sales>30 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END SALES_30
FROM 
Sales.Orders

